'''''We Could Be Heroes''''' ni film ya siporo ya documentaire yo muri [[Maroke|Maroc yo muri]] 2018 iyobowe na Hind Bensari kandi yakozwe na Habib Attia na Vibeke Vogel kuri Bullitt Films.  Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Azeddine Nouiri, wabaye nyampinga w’imikino Paralympique, watsinze imbogamizi z’umubiri zatoranijwe mu mikino Paralympike ya Rio 2016 hamwe n’inshuti ye Youssef akiri umwana. 

Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 2 Gicurasi 2018 muri Theatre ya Scotiabank .  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.   Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Jury mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Documentaire Hot Docs . Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye "Igihembo cyiza cya International Documentary Award" mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto.  Filime yatsindiye Grand Prix mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Tangier . 

